description: Officer Jenny`s Duosion is Psychic type Investigator Jenny`s main Pokémon. She uses it to help her investigate instances and crimes when Psychic Pokémon are involved. It helped rescue Pikachu, Meowth and Iris`s Axew from Leon but it then ended up getting knocked out by Leon`s Beheeyem`s Energy Ball. Officer Jenny`s Duosion used Psywave on the exit sign for each illusion instance.
name: Doublan (Junsaa)
